  <!-- EN: butchered humanlike corpse -->
  <ButcheredHumanlikeCorpseOpinion.stages.butchered_humanlike_corpse.label>屠宰了人類屍體</ButcheredHumanlikeCorpseOpinion.stages.butchered_humanlike_corpse.label>
  
  <!-- EN: catharsis -->
  <Catharsis.stages.catharsis.label>發洩情緒</Catharsis.stages.catharsis.label>
  <!-- EN: It felt good to finally unbottle my feelings. -->
  <Catharsis.stages.catharsis.description>發洩情緒後的感覺真好。</Catharsis.stages.catharsis.description>
  
  <!-- EN: colonist banished -->
  <ColonistBanished.stages.colonist_banished.label>居民被放逐</ColonistBanished.stages.colonist_banished.label>
  <!-- EN: We just banished someone. I hope they make it, but I'm worried. -->
  <ColonistBanished.stages.colonist_banished.description>我們放逐了某人。我很擔心，只希望他們能活下去。</ColonistBanished.stages.colonist_banished.description>
  
  <!-- EN: colonist banished to death -->
  <ColonistBanishedToDie.stages.colonist_banished_to_death.label>居民被放逐等死</ColonistBanishedToDie.stages.colonist_banished_to_death.label>
  <!-- EN: We banished someone in such a way that there's almost no way they'll survive. -->
  <ColonistBanishedToDie.stages.colonist_banished_to_death.description>我們以某種方式放逐某人，以至於他們幾乎無法活下來。</ColonistBanishedToDie.stages.colonist_banished_to_death.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Colonist prisoner escaped -->
  <ColonyPrisonerEscaped.stages.Colonist_prisoner_escaped.label>居民俘虜逃跑了</ColonyPrisonerEscaped.stages.Colonist_prisoner_escaped.label>
  <!-- EN: Can't we keep control of our own people? I feel like anything could happen to me here. -->
  <ColonyPrisonerEscaped.stages.Colonist_prisoner_escaped.description>我們不能控制自己的人民嗎？我覺得任何事情都可能發生在我身上。</ColonyPrisonerEscaped.stages.Colonist_prisoner_escaped.description>
  
  <!-- EN: defeated hostile leader {0} -->
  <DefeatedHostileFactionLeader.stages.defeated_hostile_leader.label>擊敗敵對派系領袖{0}</DefeatedHostileFactionLeader.stages.defeated_hostile_leader.label>
  <!-- EN: They were leading efforts to destroy us, and I took them down! -->
  <DefeatedHostileFactionLeader.stages.defeated_hostile_leader.description>他們打算殲滅我們，而我把他們打得落花流水！</DefeatedHostileFactionLeader.stages.defeated_hostile_leader.description>
  
  <!-- EN: defeated hostile leader -->
  <DefeatedHostileFactionLeaderOpinion.stages.defeated_hostile_leader.label>擊敗了敵方首領</DefeatedHostileFactionLeaderOpinion.stages.defeated_hostile_leader.label>
  
  <!-- EN: defeated insect hive -->
  <DefeatedInsectHive.stages.defeated_insect_hive.label>擊敗蟲巢</DefeatedInsectHive.stages.defeated_insect_hive.label>
  <!-- EN: The only good bug is a dead bug! -->
  <DefeatedInsectHive.stages.defeated_insect_hive.description>這些蟲子還是死的好！</DefeatedInsectHive.stages.defeated_insect_hive.description>
  
  <!-- EN: defeated mech cluster -->
  <DefeatedMechCluster.stages.defeated_mech_cluster.label>擊敗機械軍團</DefeatedMechCluster.stages.defeated_mech_cluster.label>
  <!-- EN: Blood beats metal, you damn machines! -->
  <DefeatedMechCluster.stages.defeated_mech_cluster.description>肉身擊敗金屬，你這該死的機械！</DefeatedMechCluster.stages.defeated_mech_cluster.description>
  
  <!-- EN: denied joining -->
  <DeniedJoining.stages.denied_joining.label>拒絕加入</DeniedJoining.stages.denied_joining.label>
  <!-- EN: We just denied someone's request to join us. I hope they make it. -->
  <DeniedJoining.stages.denied_joining.description>我們只是拒絕了某人加入我們的請求。我希望他們能成功。</DeniedJoining.stages.denied_joining.description>
  
  <!-- EN: failed to rescue {0} -->
  <FailedToRescueRelative.stages.failed_to_rescue.label>救援{0}失敗</FailedToRescueRelative.stages.failed_to_rescue.label>
  <!-- EN: We had a chance to rescue my relative, and failed. I could have helped! -->
  <FailedToRescueRelative.stages.failed_to_rescue.description>我們本來有機會救援我的親人，但失敗了。我本來可以救援的！</FailedToRescueRelative.stages.failed_to_rescue.description>
  
  <!-- EN: freed from slavery -->
  <FreedFromSlavery.stages.freed_from_slavery.label>擺脫奴役</FreedFromSlavery.stages.freed_from_slavery.label>
  <!-- EN: I have been freed from slavery. I'm so thankful! -->
  <FreedFromSlavery.stages.freed_from_slavery.description>我終於不再是奴隸了。十分感激！</FreedFromSlavery.stages.freed_from_slavery.description>
  
  <!-- EN: bloodlust organ harvested -->
  <HarvestedOrgan_Bloodlust.stages.bloodlust_organ_harvested.label>器官收割（嗜血）</HarvestedOrgan_Bloodlust.stages.bloodlust_organ_harvested.label>
  <!-- EN: Extracting the flesh from their bodies is so bloody and satisfying. -->
  <HarvestedOrgan_Bloodlust.stages.bloodlust_organ_harvested.description>從他們的身體中取出器官是如此的血腥而令人滿意。</HarvestedOrgan_Bloodlust.stages.bloodlust_organ_harvested.description>
  
  <!-- EN: killed someone -->
  <KilledHumanlikeBloodlust.stages.killed_someone.label>殺人</KilledHumanlikeBloodlust.stages.killed_someone.label>
  <!-- EN: I killed someone! What a rush! -->
  <KilledHumanlikeBloodlust.stages.killed_someone.description>我剛剛殺了人！太爽了！</KilledHumanlikeBloodlust.stages.killed_someone.description>
  
  <!-- EN: buried in sarcophagus -->
  <KnowBuriedInSarcophagus.stages.buried_in_sarcophagus.label>妥善安葬</KnowBuriedInSarcophagus.stages.buried_in_sarcophagus.label>
  <!-- EN: This colony buried someone in an ornamented sarcophagus. May their soul rest in peace. -->
  <KnowBuriedInSarcophagus.stages.buried_in_sarcophagus.description>這位居民被某些人安葬在棺材裡。願他們的靈魂安息。</KnowBuriedInSarcophagus.stages.buried_in_sarcophagus.description>
  
  <!-- EN: we butchered humanlike -->
  <KnowButcheredHumanlikeCorpse.stages.we_butchered_humanlike.label>我們屠宰了人類</KnowButcheredHumanlikeCorpse.stages.we_butchered_humanlike.label>
  <!-- EN: We butchered someone up like an animal. -->
  <KnowButcheredHumanlikeCorpse.stages.we_butchered_humanlike.description>我們把人類像動物般地屠宰了。</KnowButcheredHumanlikeCorpse.stages.we_butchered_humanlike.description>
  
  <!-- EN: colonist's organ harvested -->
  <KnowColonistOrganHarvested.stages.colonists_organ_harvested.label>居民的器官被摘除</KnowColonistOrganHarvested.stages.colonists_organ_harvested.label>
  <!-- EN: Someone took body parts from a colonist. It's horrible, breaking someone down for parts when they have no choice. -->
  <KnowColonistOrganHarvested.stages.colonists_organ_harvested.description>有某人摘除了居民的身體器官。他們的器官在毫無選擇的情況下被摘除，太恐怖了。</KnowColonistOrganHarvested.stages.colonists_organ_harvested.description>
  
  <!-- EN: someone's organ harvested -->
  <KnowGuestOrganHarvested.stages.someones_organ_harvested.label>有人的器官被摘除</KnowGuestOrganHarvested.stages.someones_organ_harvested.label>
  <!-- EN: The colony took body parts from a guest or prisoner. It's horrible, breaking someone down for parts when they have no choice. -->
  <KnowGuestOrganHarvested.stages.someones_organ_harvested.description>有人摘除了訪客或俘虜的身體器官。他們的器官在毫無選擇的情況下被摘除，太恐怖了。</KnowGuestOrganHarvested.stages.someones_organ_harvested.description>
  
  <!-- EN: prisoner sold -->
  <KnowPrisonerSold.stages.prisoner_sold.label>俘虜被賣掉</KnowPrisonerSold.stages.prisoner_sold.label>
  <!-- EN: This colony sold a prisoner into slavery. That's a worrying thought. -->
  <KnowPrisonerSold.stages.prisoner_sold.description>有居民把俘虜賣给奴隸商人。真是令人擔憂。</KnowPrisonerSold.stages.prisoner_sold.description>
  
  <!-- EN: my organ harvested -->
  <MyOrganHarvested.stages.my_organ_harvested.label>器官被摘除了</MyOrganHarvested.stages.my_organ_harvested.label>
  <!-- EN: The colony harvested body parts from me! They're breaking me down like an old engine! -->
  <MyOrganHarvested.stages.my_organ_harvested.description>有居民摘除了我的身體器官！他們把我當作舊引擎一樣拆解！</MyOrganHarvested.stages.my_organ_harvested.description>
  
  <!-- EN: initial hope -->
  <NewColonyHope.stages.initial_hope.label>對新家園懷抱希望</NewColonyHope.stages.initial_hope.label>
  <!-- EN: I'm getting used to this, but it's still an exciting new situation. I hope this works out... -->
  <NewColonyHope.stages.initial_hope.description>我漸漸習慣這裡了，但這個局面對我來說還是比較新的。希望一切都能順利...。</NewColonyHope.stages.initial_hope.description>
  
  <!-- EN: initial optimism -->
  <NewColonyOptimism.stages.initial_optimism.label>對新家園感到樂觀</NewColonyOptimism.stages.initial_optimism.label>
  <!-- EN: It's a tough situation, but I'm excited to be founding a new settlement. -->
  <NewColonyOptimism.stages.initial_optimism.description>我們剛剛降落在這裡，情况不是很好，但是我仍然對建立一個新家園感到激動。</NewColonyOptimism.stages.initial_optimism.description>
  
  <!-- EN: nuzzled -->
  <Nuzzled.stages.nuzzled.label>動物撒嬌</Nuzzled.stages.nuzzled.label>
  <!-- EN: A cute animal nuzzled me. -->
  <Nuzzled.stages.nuzzled.description>一隻可愛的動物對我撒嬌。</Nuzzled.stages.nuzzled.description>
  
  <!-- EN: observed corpse -->
  <ObservedLayingCorpse.stages.observed_corpse.label>目睹屍體</ObservedLayingCorpse.stages.observed_corpse.label>
  <!-- EN: I saw a dead body laying on the ground. It was disturbing. -->
  <ObservedLayingCorpse.stages.observed_corpse.description>我看見一具躺在地上的屍體。</ObservedLayingCorpse.stages.observed_corpse.description>
  
  <!-- EN: observed rotting corpse -->
  <ObservedLayingRottingCorpse.stages.observed_rotting_corpse.label>目睹腐爛的屍體</ObservedLayingRottingCorpse.stages.observed_rotting_corpse.label>
  <!-- EN: I saw a rotting corpse laying on the ground. It was disgusting. -->
  <ObservedLayingRottingCorpse.stages.observed_rotting_corpse.description>我看見一具躺在地上的腐爛屍體。真令人作嘔。</ObservedLayingRottingCorpse.stages.observed_rotting_corpse.description>
  
  <!-- EN: on duty -->
  <OnDuty.stages.on_duty.label>值班</OnDuty.stages.on_duty.label>
  <!-- EN: I have a job to do. -->
  <OnDuty.stages.on_duty.description>我有一份工作。</OnDuty.stages.on_duty.description>
  
  <!-- EN: prisoner banished to death -->
  <PrisonerBanishedToDie.stages.prisoner_banished_to_death.label>被放逐俘虜死亡</PrisonerBanishedToDie.stages.prisoner_banished_to_death.label>
  <!-- EN: We banished a prisoner in such a way that there's almost no way they'll survive. -->
  <PrisonerBanishedToDie.stages.prisoner_banished_to_death.description>我們以某種方式放逐某人，以至於他們幾乎無法活下來。</PrisonerBanishedToDie.stages.prisoner_banished_to_death.description>
  
  <!-- EN: prisoner released -->
  <ReleasedHealthyPrisoner.stages.prisoner_released.label>俘虜被釋放</ReleasedHealthyPrisoner.stages.prisoner_released.label>
  <!-- EN: We released a healthy prisoner. It feels good to know we even treat prisoners well. -->
  <ReleasedHealthyPrisoner.stages.prisoner_released.description>我們釋放了一位健康的俘虜。我們能善待俘虜真是太好了。</ReleasedHealthyPrisoner.stages.prisoner_released.description>
  
  <!-- EN: rescued -->
  <Rescued.stages.rescued.label>被救援</Rescued.stages.rescued.label>
  <!-- EN: I was rescued! I almost thought I was done for back there. I'm so thankful. -->
  <Rescued.stages.rescued.description>我被救援了！我幾乎以為我回不來了。感激不盡。</Rescued.stages.rescued.description>
  
  <!-- EN: rescued {0} -->
  <RescuedRelative.stages.rescued.label>救援了{0}</RescuedRelative.stages.rescued.label>
  <!-- EN: We rescued one of my relatives. Finally, I can breathe a sigh of relief. -->
  <RescuedRelative.stages.rescued.description>我們救援了我的親人。我終於可以鬆一口氣。</RescuedRelative.stages.rescued.description>
  
  <!-- EN: disturbed sleep -->
  <SleepDisturbed.stages.disturbed_sleep.label>輾轉難眠</SleepDisturbed.stages.disturbed_sleep.label>
  <!-- EN: I was disturbed during sleep by people moving around nearby. A private room would solve this. -->
  <SleepDisturbed.stages.disturbed_sleep.description>我睡覺時有人在附近走來走去。私人臥室可以解決這個問題。</SleepDisturbed.stages.disturbed_sleep.description>
  
  <!-- EN: slept in the cold -->
  <SleptInCold.stages.slept_in_the_cold.label>睡在寒冷的地方</SleptInCold.stages.slept_in_the_cold.label>
  <!-- EN: I had to sleep in the cold. We really need some heaters. -->
  <SleptInCold.stages.slept_in_the_cold.description>我睡在寒冷的地方。我們真的需要一些電暖爐。</SleptInCold.stages.slept_in_the_cold.description>
  
  <!-- EN: slept in the heat -->
  <SleptInHeat.stages.slept_in_the_heat.label>睡在炎熱的地方</SleptInHeat.stages.slept_in_the_heat.label>
  <!-- EN: I had to sleep in unbearable heat. Can't we have air conditioning? -->
  <SleptInHeat.stages.slept_in_the_heat.description>我睡在炎熱的地方。我們不能裝台冷氣嗎？</SleptInHeat.stages.slept_in_the_heat.description>
  
  <!-- EN: slept on ground -->
  <SleptOnGround.stages.slept_on_ground.label>睡在地上</SleptOnGround.stages.slept_on_ground.label>
  <!-- EN: I had to sleep on the ground like an animal. -->
  <SleptOnGround.stages.slept_on_ground.description>我像動物般地睡在地上。</SleptOnGround.stages.slept_on_ground.description>
  
  <!-- EN: slept outside -->
  <SleptOutside.stages.slept_outside.label>睡在外面</SleptOutside.stages.slept_outside.label>
  <!-- EN: I had to sleep outdoors without any protection from the elements. -->
  <SleptOutside.stages.slept_outside.description>我睡在外面，沒有東西能夠保護我。</SleptOutside.stages.slept_outside.description>
  
  <!-- EN: soaking wet -->
  <SoakingWet.stages.soaking_wet.label>溼透</SoakingWet.stages.soaking_wet.label>
  <!-- EN: I'm soaking wet. -->
  <SoakingWet.stages.soaking_wet.description>我全身溼透了。</SoakingWet.stages.soaking_wet.description>
  
  <!-- EN: eager to travel -->
  <TravelAnticipation.stages.eager_to_travel.label>旅行的憧憬</TravelAnticipation.stages.eager_to_travel.label>
  <!-- EN: I've been preparing this caravan for a while. I'm looking forward to the upcoming journey. -->
  <TravelAnticipation.stages.eager_to_travel.description>我為這趟旅程花了不少心思作準備。我很期待出發。</TravelAnticipation.stages.eager_to_travel.description>
  <!-- EN: excited to travel -->
  <TravelAnticipation.stages.excited_to_travel.label>旅行的興奮</TravelAnticipation.stages.excited_to_travel.label>
  <!-- EN: So much thought and preparation have gone into this adventure. I can't wait to set off! -->
  <TravelAnticipation.stages.excited_to_travel.description>我對這次冒險充滿各種想法和準備。我等不及要出發啦!</TravelAnticipation.stages.excited_to_travel.description>
  
  <!-- EN: was imprisoned -->
  <WasImprisoned.stages.was_imprisoned.label>被囚禁</WasImprisoned.stages.was_imprisoned.label>
  <!-- EN: The colony had me in jail for a while, like a caged animal. -->
  <WasImprisoned.stages.was_imprisoned.description>有居民把我關進監獄一段時間了，就像是籠中的動物。</WasImprisoned.stages.was_imprisoned.description>
  
  <!-- EN: witnessed ally's death -->
  <WitnessedDeathAlly.stages.witnessed_allys_death.label>目睹同伴死亡</WitnessedDeathAlly.stages.witnessed_allys_death.label>
  <!-- EN: I saw one of my people die. They were alive one moment, and dead the next. -->
  <WitnessedDeathAlly.stages.witnessed_allys_death.description>我看見我們的人死了。他們剛才還活著的，下一秒就死了。</WitnessedDeathAlly.stages.witnessed_allys_death.description>
  
  <!-- EN: witnessed death with bloodlust -->
  <WitnessedDeathBloodlust.stages.witnessed_death_with_bloodlust.label>嗜血狂怒目睹死亡</WitnessedDeathBloodlust.stages.witnessed_death_with_bloodlust.label>
  <!-- EN: I saw someone die! That was intense! -->
  <WitnessedDeathBloodlust.stages.witnessed_death_with_bloodlust.description>我看見有人死了！真是太刺激了！</WitnessedDeathBloodlust.stages.witnessed_death_with_bloodlust.description>
  
  <!-- EN: witnessed family member's death -->
  <WitnessedDeathFamily.stages.witnessed_family_members_death.label>目睹家人死亡</WitnessedDeathFamily.stages.witnessed_family_members_death.label>
  <!-- EN: I saw a member of my family die. My own flesh and blood... -->
  <WitnessedDeathFamily.stages.witnessed_family_members_death.description>我看見我的家人死亡。我的親人啊...</WitnessedDeathFamily.stages.witnessed_family_members_death.description>
  
  <!-- EN: witnessed outsider's death -->
  <WitnessedDeathNonAlly.stages.witnessed_outsiders_death.label>目睹陌生人死亡</WitnessedDeathNonAlly.stages.witnessed_outsiders_death.label>
  <!-- EN: I saw someone die. They were alive one moment, and dead the next. -->
  <WitnessedDeathNonAlly.stages.witnessed_outsiders_death.description>我看見有人死了。他們剛才還活著的，下一秒就死了。</WitnessedDeathNonAlly.stages.witnessed_outsiders_death.description>
  
